description: A collection of circles in a thin, tilted rectangular formation; there is also  a four-pointed star extending upwards from the top left corner of the rectangular formation and a three-pointed star extending outwards from the top right corner. Each circle has a different number in the center denoting how many lines stem from that point. There is a very pale, very small greenish-yellow triangle at the bottom of the rectangular formation.

author.name: VertexArchive
